OL,3,C'Dangerous and dehumanising' corridor
OL,4,Ccare has become 'endemic', survey finds
OL,6,FCare for patients in emergency
OL,7,Fdepartment corridors in Wales has
OL,8,Fbecome 'endemic', according to the
OL,9,FRoyal College for Emergency Medicine.
OL,11,FThe College, which represents
OL,12,Femergency clinicians across Wales, has
OL,13,Ffound every emergency department
OL,14,Facross the country is having to treat
OL,15,Fpatients in corridors.
OL,17,FIt is now calling on the Welsh
OL,18,Fgovernment to prevent corridor care,
OL,19,Fbranding it "dangerous, degrading,
OL,20,Fdehumanising".
