OL,3,C'Dangerous and dehumanising' corridor
OL,4,Ccare has become 'endemic', survey finds
OL,6,FDr Rob Perry, RCEM vice president of
OL,7,FWales, said, "Recently the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment said that compromising the
OL,9,Fquality of care, privacy, or dignity
OL,10,Fof patients only happens on 'occasions
OL,11,Fwhen the NHS faces exceptional
OL,12,Fpressure'.
OL,14,F"Well, our research clearly shows that
OL,15,Fexceptional pressure is now the
OL,16,Feveryday norm in Wales' Emergency
OL,17,FDepartments (EDs).
