OL,3,C'Dangerous and dehumanising' corridor
OL,4,Ccare has become 'endemic', survey finds
OL,6,F"And this must not be dismissed as
OL,7,Fjust being down to but the annual
OL,8,Fseasonal upsurge. I am confident the
OL,9,Fresults would be similar whichever
OL,10,Ftime of the year we undertook this
OL,11,Fsurvey.
OL,13,F"These findings should shock and shame
OL,14,Fthe Government into action.
OL,16,F"So-called 'corridor care' is
OL,17,Fdangerous, degrading, dehumanising and
OL,18,Fit is now endemic here in Wales.
