OL,6,FA spokesman for the Welsh Government
OL,7,Fsaid: "We do not endorse the routine
OL,8,Fcare or treatment of individuals in
OL,9,Fnon-clinical or unsuitable
OL,10,Fenvironments, nor any situations where
OL,11,Fthe quality of care, privacy, or
OL,12,Fdignity of patients is compromised.
OL,14,F"However, there are occasions when the
OL,15,FNHS faces exceptional pressures, such
OL,16,Fas during periods of increased demand
OL,17,For public health emergencies.
